OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFormer Pope was 'powerful  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpresence', says archbishop 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pope Benedict was still a "powerful    
OL,6, presence" in the Vatican despite his   
OL,7, retirement - the most senior British   
OL,8, figure there has told the BBC.         
OL,10,FThe comments, by Archbishop Paul       
OL,11,FGallagher, have come as the reigning   
OL,12,Fpope, Francis, makes final preparations
OL,13,Ffor the unusual event of a pontiff     
OL,14,Fpresiding at the funeral of his        
OL,15,Fpredecessor.                           
OL,17,FAfter Thursday's burial of former pope 
OL,18,FBenedict XVI, there will be just one   
OL,19,Fman wearing white in the corridors of  
OL,20,Fthe Vatican for the first time in      
OL,21,Fnearly a decade.                       
